        <ul style="margin-top:1rem;">
          <li><a href="/services/ceiling-insulation/">Ceiling insulation</a> &mdash; the biggest single-step upgrade</li>
          <li><a href="/services/wall-insulation/">Wall insulation</a> &mdash; cavity injection for existing homes</li>
          <li><a href="/services/underfloor-insulation/">Underfloor insulation</a> &mdash; bulk batts and reflective foil</li>
          <li><a href="/services/roof-insulation/">Roof insulation &amp; sarking</a> &mdash; radiant barrier under metal roofs</li>
          <li><a href="/services/acoustic-insulation/">Acoustic insulation</a> &mdash; party walls and home theatres</li>
          <li><a href="/beaconsfield/">Beaconsfield insulation</a> &mdash; service area landing page</li>
          <li><a href="/cardinia-shire/">All Cardinia Shire</a> &mdash; Pakenham, Officer, Cardinia Lakes, Heritage Springs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--ink, #0F2A47);color:#fff;">
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2 style="color:#fff;">Free quote &mdash; VEU rebate-eligible insulation.</h2>
      <p style="opacity:0.85;max-width:50rem;margin:1rem auto 2rem;">
        Ceiling, wall, underfloor and acoustic insulation across
        Beaconsfield and Cardinia Shire. Accredited Victorian Energy
        Upgrades installer &mdash; rebates lodged in the quote, AS 3999
        install standard, R-values matched to NCC Climate Zone 6.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a fixed quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
